OL,3,CEx-priest claims asylum seekers
OL,4,Cbrought 'week-in, week-out' for
OL,5,Cconversion
OL,7,FMr Firth left the church in 2020 and
OL,8,Fis now a vicar for the Free Church of
OL,9,FEngland.
OL,11,FHe told the committee that when he
OL,12,Fcame to St Cuthbert's in 2018 he found
OL,13,Fthere was a "surprising number" of
OL,14,Fbaptisms going forward with asylum
OL,15,Fseekers.
OL,17,FHe said that he started to "look into"
OL,18,Fthe trend, after honouring the
OL,19,Fbaptisms that were already in process.
