OL,3,CEx-priest claims asylum seekers
OL,4,Cbrought 'week-in, week-out' for
OL,5,Cconversion
OL,7,F"I started to look into it a bit
OL,8,Ffurther," he explained. "After those
OL,9,Fbaptisms, week-in, week-out,
OL,10,Fsignificant groups of mainly Iranian
OL,11,Fand Syrian young male asylum seekers
OL,12,Fwere being brought to me in sizeable
OL,13,Fcohorts."
OL,15,FMr Firth said the cohorts were "six or
OL,16,Fseven" people "every two or three
OL,17,Fweeks".
OL,19,F"At a time six or seven people brought
OL,20,Fto me by people saying these people
OL,21,Fneed baptism," he said.
