OL,7,FMr Firth said that he did not have
OL,8,Faccess to the parish registers, so was
OL,9,Fnot familiar with those figures.
OL,11,FHe said he "pressed a pause button on
OL,12,Fthe process" of baptism requests after
OL,13,Fbecoming concerned.
OL,15,F"There is a difference between the
OL,16,Fnumber of people being brought to me
OL,17,Fto request baptism, and the actual
OL,18,Fnumber of baptisms that happened," Mr
OL,19,FFirth said.
