OL,3,CEx-priest claims asylum seekers
OL,4,Cbrought 'week-in, week-out' for
OL,5,Cconversion
OL,7,FHe said that he made sure the baptism
OL,8,Fprocess was "rigorous" after taking on
OL,9,Fthe job, and "that made the numbers
OL,10,Ffall off a cliff".
OL,12,F"You try to press a pause button which
OL,13,Fis to make sure that people are
OL,14,Frequested to come to church, start
OL,15,Fgetting involved and attending church
OL,16,Fregularly and events," he added. "That
OL,17,Fwas the thing that kind of made the
OL,18,Fnumbers fall off a cliff in a sense
OL,19,Fbecause those people melted away
OL,20,Freally.
