OL,7,F"We are extremely proud of St
OL,8,FCuthbert's and the work the church
OL,9,Fdoes to ensure asylum seekers and
OL,10,Frefugees are welcomed and supported in
OL,11,FDarlington.
OL,13,F"The baptism records before and during
OL,14,FMr Firth's time at St Cuthbert's, and
OL,15,Fthe testimony of local church members,
OL,16,Fdo not accord with Mr Firth's evidence.
