OL,7,F"The parish records show that since
OL,8,F2014 a maximum of 15 out of a total of
OL,9,F189 people baptised at St Cuthbert's
OL,10,Fmay have been asylum seekers, 7 of
OL,11,Fwhom were baptised by Mr Firth himself.
