OL,7,F"In the four years prior to Mr Firth's
OL,8,Farrival as Priest in Charge in 2018
OL,9,Fonly six people who may have been
OL,10,Fasylum seekers were baptised. As
OL,11,FPriest in Charge it was his
OL,12,Fresponsibility to check the
OL,13,Fauthenticity of candidates and it is
OL,14,Fsurprising that, as he acknowledged to
OL,15,Fthe committee, he did not report any
OL,16,Fsign of anything amiss, at the time.
